org.orgName: District Court of the United States for the Western District of Washington

body.p: IN THE DISTRICT COURT OF THE UNITED STATES IN AND FOR THE WESTERN DISTRICT OF WASHINGTON, NORTHERN DIVISION.
In the Matter of the Petition of } No. 5959 Hosaye Sakaguchi, } ORDER for a Writ of Habeas Corpus.

Upon stipulation of Counsel, it is by the Court ordered, and the Court does hereby ORDER, that the original record of the United States Immigration Office at Seattle, filed herein as part of the return of the Commissioner of Immigration, be transmitted by the Clerk to the United States Circuit Court of Appeals as an original exhibit and that the same need not be printed
Dated in open court this 20 day of June, 1921. Edward E. Cushman Judge.
